'''Karu Nelbin''' was a [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] and the original owner of the ''[[Nightcast]]''.
Nelbin was [[Death/Legends|killed]] by professional [[Assassin/Legends|assassin]] [[Callandri]], who then kept the ''Nightcast'' as her own [[Starship/Legends|ship]].<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

